A personal account refers to a central wallet, which is saved by Theia for your private key. In a central wallet, there is no loss of wallet that cannot be recovered, and can be verified to retrieve your wallet and allow you to experience more services. Private Key Wallet The private key wallet is to go to the central wallet, in the central wallet, all user authentication content, such as trading passwords, private keys, mnemonics, etc. are stored in the user\'s mobile phone local, not stored in the centralized server. If the user mistakenly deletes the wallet, forgets to back up the private key or mnemonics, will not be able to retrieve the wallet. Advantages Your private keys are 100% managed by yourself Defect There\'s mining fee. The transaction rate is slow. How to back up your wallet In case your phone loses or forgets your password, mnemonics can be used for your wallet or money. Please click on the mnemonics in order to make sure your backup mnemonics are filled in correctly Confirm the notation words which helps you remember your wallet Now write down these words.
